'''Itaquitinga''' is a city located in the state of [[Pernambuco]], [[Brazil]]. Located at 84&nbsp;km away from [[Recife]], capital of the state of Pernambuco. Has an estimated ([[Brazilian Institute of Geography and Statistics|Ibge 2009]]) population of 15.507 inhabitants.
==Geography== * State - [[Pernambuco]] * Region - [[Zona da Mata (coastal)|Zona da mata Pernambucana]] * Boundaries - [[Condado, Pernambuco|Condado]] ('''N'''); [[Igarassu, Pernambuco|Igarassu]] ('''S'''); [[Goiana]] ('''E'''); [[Nazaré da Mata]] and [[Tracunhaém]] ('''W''') * Area - 103.44&nbsp;km<sup>2</sup> * Elevation - 88 m * Hidrography - [[Goiana River]] * Vegetation - [[Subcaducifólia]] forest * Clima - Hot tropical and humid * Annual average temperature - 23.3 c * Distance to [[Recife]] - 84&nbsp;km
==Economy== The main economic activities in '''Itaquitinga''' are based in [[agribusiness]], especially [[sugarcane]] (over 477,000 tons) and [[livestock]] such as [[cattle]] and [[chickens]].
